data.description: FIXER UPPER!  CASH OR CONVENTIONAL BUYERS ONLY.  SELLER WANTS IT SOLD.   Now more than ever is the time to own this charming single story, 3 bedroom, 2 baths, 1761 sq. ft, home.  This home provides  the perfect blend of comfort and space.  The corner lot ensures a sense of openness and provides additional space for landscaping possibilities.  With its functional layout, remodeled features and spacious yard, this home presents a wonderful opportunity to make it your new home or rental income property.    Step inside to discover the heart of the home, a thoughtfully remodeled kitchen, featuring granite countertops, double sink and a newer stainless steel stove.  The kitchen has been expanded, creating an inviting area to cook all your favorite meals.   The living space is highlighted by a generous bonus/family room, which was once the garage and has been transformed to accommodate your entertainment needs.  This versatile room enhances the overall living space and provides ample room for relaxation or gatherings.  Step outside and experience the expansive backyard, an ideal setting for parties, barbecues and outdoor activities.  This home has much to offer.
